<div class="row">
    <div class="col-3"></div>
    <div class="col-6 ">
        <form action="/users/signUp" method="POST" class="signIn-form">
            <h3 class="font-weight-bold mt-5 mb-5">建立你的帳戶</h3>
            <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" name="name" class="form-control radious" placeholder="姓名">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <input type="email" name="email" class="form-control  radious" placeholder="信箱">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <input type="password" name="password" class="form-control  radious" placeholder="密碼">
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <input type="password" name="password_confirm" class="form-control  radious" placeholder="確認密碼">
            </div>

            <p class="mt-5 mb-1">如果註冊，即表示你同意<span><a href="">服務條款</a></span>和<span><a href="">隱私政策</a></span>，包括<span><a
                        href="">Cookie
                        使用政策</a></span>。提供電子郵件或電話號碼時，其他人可透過電子郵件或電話找到你。<span><a href="">隱私選項</a></span></p>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-block  radious">註冊</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div class="col-3"></div>
</div>